Azimio coalition led by presidential candidate Raila Odinga and his running mate  Martha Karua on Thursday held campaigns in Kirinyaga County. Kirinyaga is the home county of the Azimio presidential running mate. This marks the third day of Azimio campaign tours in the MT Kenya region. Present were Suna East MP Junet Mohamed, Kitui Governor Charity Ngilu, Former Gatanga MP Charity Ngilu, former Gatanga MP Peter Kenneth and  Kieni MP Kanini Kega among many other leaders. Interior PS Karanja Kibicho was present. On Wednesday, the team sold their manifesto to Kiambu County residents.